snippet.textDisplay:
Gaddiey (motor car)means spirit
 The poet being the manifestation of physical body urges the Gaddiey/spirit to find our owner/mechanic  who can drive us who can repair us who can guard us who can wash us and who can lead us towards the perfection. Basically this Kalam is highly mystical/sofiana. And the rendition is quite in accordance with the thematic essence of the song. 🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏
